        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p> The nightwalker points at one creature it can see within 300 feet of it. The target must succeed on a [[/save wis 21 format=long]] or take [[/damage 6d12 type=necrotic average=true]] damage and become &amp;Reference[frightened]{frightened} until the end of the nightwalker’s next turn. While &amp;Reference[frightened]{frightened} in this way, the creature is also &amp;Reference[paralyzed]{paralyzed}. If a target’s saving throw is successful, the target is immune to the nightwalker’s Finger of Doom for the next 24 hours.</p>\n</section>\nThe [[lookup @name]] uses [[lookup @item.name]] and a save is required.\n</div>",
